ejezd\u011bte do servisu zbyte\u010dn\u011b se v\u0161emi vozy. Na\u0161i technici prov\u011b\u0159\u00ed cel\u00fd vozov\u00fd park p\u0159\u00edmo v prostor\u00e1ch va\u0161\u00ed firmy. K n\u00e1m pak p\u0159ijedete jen s t\u011bmi auty, u kter\u00fdch se projev\u00ed z\u00e1vada.<\/div><div class=\"btn-align\"><a href=\"\/autoservis-pro-firmy\/\" title=\"zjistit v\u00edce\" class=\"btn btn-inverse btn-normal btn-primary \" target=\"_self\">zjistit v\u00edce<\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div><!-- \/Service Box --><\/section><\/div><div class=\"span3 \"><section class=\"lazy-load-box  trigger effect-slidefromright\" data-delay=\"200\" data-speed=\"800\" style=\"-webkit-transition: all 800ms ease; -moz-transition: all 800ms ease; -ms-transition: all 800ms ease; -o-transition: all 800ms ease; transition: all 800ms ease;\"><div class=\"service-box style_1\"><figure class=\"icon\"><img src=\"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/wp-content\/themes\/theme53985\/images\/icon3.png\" alt=\"\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"service-box_body\"><h2 class=\"title\">P\u0159ezut\u00ed<\/h2><h5 class=\"sub-title\">PNEUMATIK<\/h5><div class=\"service-box_txt\">P\u0159ezouv\u00e1me pneumatiky a\u017e do pr\u016fm\u011bru 23\u201d a to u\u017e za p\u016fl hodiny. Na p\u0159\u00e1n\u00ed v\u00e1m tak\u00e9 zajist\u00edme nov\u00e9 pneumatiky r\u016fzn\u00fdch typ\u016f a zna\u010dek.<\/div><div class=\"btn-align\"><a href=\"\/prezuti-a-prodej-pneumatik-pro-vas-vuz\/\" title=\"Zjistit v\u00edce\" class=\"btn btn-inverse btn-normal btn-primary \" target=\"_self\">Zjistit v\u00edce<\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div><!-- \/Service Box --><\/section><\/div><div class=\"span3 \"><section class=\"lazy-load-box  trigger effect-slidefromright\" data-delay=\"400\" data-speed=\"800\" style=\"-webkit-transition: all 800ms ease; -moz-transition: all 800ms ease; -ms-transition: all 800ms ease; -o-transition: all 800ms ease; transition: all 800ms ease;\"><div class=\"service-box style_1\"><figure class=\"icon\"><img src=\"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/wp-content\/themes\/theme53985\/images\/icon4.png\" alt=\"\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"service-box_body\"><h2 class=\"title\">Dopl\u0148kov\u00e9<\/h2><h5 class=\"sub-title\">slu\u017eby<\/h5><div class=\"service-box_txt\">Nab\u00edz\u00edme celou \u0159adu dopl\u0148kov\u00fdch slu\u017eeb, nap\u0159\u00edklad diagnostiku vozidla, p\u0159\u00edpravu i kompletn\u00ed realizaci STK, nebo servis a pln\u011bn\u00ed klimatizac\u00ed. Ve\u0161ker\u00e1 p\u00e9\u010de o v\u00e1\u0161 v\u016fz na jednom m\u00edst\u011b.<\/div><div class=\"btn-align\"><a href=\"\/dalsi-sluzby\/\" title=\"Zjistit v\u00edce\" class=\"btn btn-inverse btn-normal btn-primary \" target=\"_self\">Zjistit v\u00edce<\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div><!-- \/Service Box --><\/section><\/div><\/div><!-- .row (end) --><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"span6 \"><section class=\"lazy-load-box  trigger effect-slidefromleft\" data-delay=\"200\" data-speed=\"800\" style=\"-webkit-transition: all 800ms ease; -moz-transition: all 800ms ease; -ms-transition: all 800ms ease; -o-transition: all 800ms ease; transition: all 800ms ease;\">\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1957\" src=\"http:\/\/jasservis.cz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/o-nas.jpg\" alt=\"J&amp;S servis o n\u00e1s\" \/><\/p>\n<\/section><\/div><div class=\"span6 \"><section class=\"lazy-load-box  trigger effect-slidefromright\" data-delay=\"200\" data-speed=\"800\" style=\"-webkit-transition: all 800ms ease; -moz-transition: all 800ms ease; -ms-transition: all 800ms ease; -o-transition: all 800ms ease; transition: all 800ms ease;\"><div class=\"service-box style_2\"><div class=\"service-box_body\"><h2 class=\"title\">J&amp;S servis Praha - z\u00e1pad<\/h2><h5 class=\"sub-title\">Kompletn\u00ed zna\u010dkov\u00e1 p\u00e9\u010de o v\u00e1\u0161 v\u016fz<\/h5><div class=\"service-box_txt\">Neztr\u00e1cejte \u010das p\u0159ej\u00ed\u017ed\u011bn\u00edm. O v\u00e1\u0161 osobn\u00ed \u010di firemn\u00ed v\u016fz se postar\